{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6bffbd8f07","title":"致彭德怀电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1f1ae30683","index":0,"year":1936,"month":8,"day":13,"articleId":"6bffbd8f07"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4e5f5f3759","type":"paragraph","text":"致彭德怀电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"6bffbd8f07"},{"id":"eabf766190","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年8月13日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"6bffbd8f07"},{"id":"0a7ef97c12","type":"paragraph","text":"红一方面军八月至九月中旬仍以训练休养生息为宜，同时求部分扩红，巩固现有根据地，形成强有力的中心力量。准备九月中旬以后向西出动一步，仍以休养、训练、扩红、扩大根据地为目的，对东北军何柱国、董英斌P二部全力进行统一战线工作。当红二四方面军甘南任务完成，九、十月间北上时，红一方面军便以军容整壮之姿态与红二、红四方面军在固原、海原地区会合。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"6bffbd8f07"},{"id":"864b3be452","type":"paragraph","text":"[11这是毛泽东致彭德怀电的主要内容。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"6bffbd8f07"},{"id":"ae8ac99df2","type":"paragraph","text":"21董英斌，当时任国民党军西北“总”第二路军第七纵队司令、东北军第五十七军军长。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"6bffbd8f07"}],"page":{"id":"0063319954","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"6bffbd8f07","start":61,"end":61}}}},"__N_SSG":true}